title: NeNe Leakes Interview and More
itunes:title: NeNe Leakes Interview and More
description:
Today on the show we had special guest and first timer Nene Leakes stop by where she spoke about "Real Housewives of Atlanta" Wendy Williams and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to James Dolan and the New York Knicks administration for treating their number 1 fan Spike Lee bad at the game and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
